          "question": "<p>It was observed that a pencil sharpener gets attracted by both the poles of a magnet although its body is made of plastic. Name a material that might have been used to make some part of it.</p>",
          "id": 72580,
          "options_data": [],
          "solution_data": [
            {
              "id": 19447,
              "solution": "<p>A pencil sharpener gets attracted by both the poles of a magnetic although its body is made of plastic, because the pencil sharpener contain some iron particles.</p>"
            }
          ],
          "num_solutions_data": [],
          "alternate_solutions_data": [],
          "marks": 0,
